@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<style>
    
    body {
        background-color: #fff8f8;
        font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        color: #333;
    }

    h1, h2 {
        font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
        color: #ff6f91;
    }

    .container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background: white;
        border-radius: 15px;
        box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    p, li {
        color: #555;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.8;
    }

    ul {
        margin-left: 20px;
    }

    footer {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #777;
    }
</style>

<div class="container">
    <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
    <p>Welcome to MyBlogSpace! Your privacy is important to us, and we are committed to protecting your personal information. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your data when you visit our blog.</p>

    <h2>What Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Personal information you provide when subscribing to our newsletter (e.g., email address).</li>
        <li>Browser and device information collected through cookies for analytics purposes.</li>
        <li>Any data you provide when leaving comments or contacting us.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>We use your data for the following purposes:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>To send you updates about new posts, events, or features.</li>
        <li>To improve the functionality and user experience of our blog.</li>
        <li>To respond to your inquiries or comments.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Your Privacy Choices</h2>
    <p>You have the right to opt out of our newsletter at any time. Additionally, you can disable cookies through your browser settings. For any concerns regarding your data, feel free to contact us.</p>

    <h2>Copyright Notice</h2>
    <p>All content on this blog, including text, images, and design, is © 2024 MyBlogSpace. Unauthorized use or reproduction of this material is strictly prohibited without prior permission from the blog owner.</p>
    <p>If you wish to share our content, please provide proper credit and a link back to our website.</p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or need further assistance, you can contact us at:</p>
    <p><strong>Email:</strong> support@myblogspace.com</p>

    <footer>
        <p>© 2024 MyBlogSpace. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</div>
